title: Ohio Valley Conference preseason men's team
text:
Ohio Valley Conference preseason men’s team By -   
NASHVILLE, Tenn. (AP) - The 2015-16 Ohio Valley Conference preseason men’s basketball team as voted on by coaches and sports information directors and released Tuesday: 
G Alex Anderson, UT Martin 
G/F Trae Anderson, Eastern Illinois 
G Brent Arrington, Morehead St. 
G Craig Bradshaw, Belmont 
G Antonius Cleveland, SE Missouri 
C Chris Horton, Austin Peay 
F Twymond Howard, UT Martin 
G Cornell Johnston, Eastern Illinois 
F Jeffery Moss, Murray State 
___ 
Preseason OVC Player of the Year: Craig Bradshaw, Belmont
